message:
On October 31st a new book about human trafficking will be released. Dr. Kimberly Mehlman-Orozco's book covers all aspects of human trafficking. This book will become a great tool in educating people about this horrific crime that happens in our own backyard. 
You can pre-order your copy today.

attachments.media_description: Hidden in Plain Sight: America's Slaves of the New Millennium
